{"tid":964443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳浩天：獨派不應再停留於社運 要為流血革命做準備，要為建國執政做準備","createTime":"2019-01-01T10:22:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T14:49:54.000Z","uid":133680,"like":43,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"caa0050d3d240c6abdf14b1bb9eed4fb10addfe0","tid":964443,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:22:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1477690/民族黨今晚集會%20陳浩天︰為革命做好準備\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1477690%2F%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E9%BB%A8%E4%BB%8A%E6%99%9A%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%2520%E9%99%B3%E6%B5%A9%E5%A4%A9%EF%B8%B0%E7%82%BA%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD%E5%81%9A%E5%A5%BD%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99&d=gU8nps7zQsY9NRt2s4Sj8JWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=6dd4937f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1477690/民族黨今晚集會%20陳浩天︰為革命做好準備</a><br />\n1000人出席集會，但他現時估計應有數千人出席。他說，有些本土派的支持者向他反映，希望有新一次的衝擊行動，但他表示，獨立派應走上健康的路，不止再停留於社運，而是要為執政作好準備。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，集會糾察不會阻止及限制參與者有後續行動，但他評估今晚發生衝擊的機會不大，又說在集會尾聲，將公布該黨的短、中、長期計劃，包括未來發展方向。<br />\n<br />\n陳浩天表示，五位被撤銷立法會參選資格的候選人，包括本土民主前線梁天琦、中出羊子等，都會上台發言，各大專院校學生會、熱血公民及青年新政都會派代表出席。"},{"pid":"8dff239d1b10cf189e87367dc4bf75095bb4e70a","tid":964443,"uid":133680,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:23:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3s9E3vH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3s9E3vH.gif&h=387fa7b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kQxSD34.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkQxSD34.gif&h=69e525c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d51c2e7b09ead844604601fe517262ddc1749f12","tid":964443,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:23:36.000Z","msg":"獨立派應走上健康的路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c3233047efb9b3ea83a4194d8e175b42bbb0f6","tid":964443,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,